import { 
    Navbar, 
    Nav, 
    NavDropdown, 
    Container } from 'react-bootstrap'

import OffCanvas from './OffCanvas'

import '../styles/Header.css'

export default function Header({ children }){

    return (
        <>
            <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="light" variant="light">
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav  className="my-2">
                            <Nav.Link href="#features">Features</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#pricing">Pricing</Nav.Link>
                            <NavDropdown title="Dropdown" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Another action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Separated link</NavDropdown.Item>
                            </NavDropdown>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                    
                    <Nav className="brand-nav me-auto">
                        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Cornelia's</Navbar.Brand>
                    </Nav>

                    <Nav className="right-nav">
                        <Nav.Link className="bi bi-search" href="#memes"></Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link className="bi bi-cart4" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvas-cart"></Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link className="bi bi-person" href="#deets"></Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Container>
                
            </Navbar>
            <OffCanvas id="offcanvas-cart" title="Cart" label="offcanvas-cart-label" >

            </OffCanvas>
        </>
    )
}
